{"id": "ChIJQwN27jnGwoARdtPXUkXD740", "rating": 4.5, "userRatingCount": 1828, "displayName": {"text": "Little Tokyo Galleria", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJQwN27jnGwoARdtPXUkXD740/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WSE1qTmxNWFZIUTNWeVgxSXlUMFJ3Y1U5U2FHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "It’s been brought to life after all the flea markets that have been taking place there very nice to discover new shops, cafes and the ambience is nice compared to overpopulated malls.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It’s been brought to life after all the flea markets that have been taking place there very nice to discover new shops, cafes and the ambience is nice compared to overpopulated malls.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Michelle insauste", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105902153432160041680/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWE-NPfHYjsTUx1Z8_4vGlGzpmvzV8QTyip7LJEcXtyCONLiHADaw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-05T22:54:09.956624273Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WSE1qTmxNWFZIUTNWeVgxSXlUMFJ3Y1U5U2FHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WSE1qTmxNWFZIUTNWeVgxSXlUMFJ3Y1U5U2FHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c639ee760343:0x8defc34552d7d376"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQwN27jnGwoARdtPXUkXD740/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkS2F6WmlhR1I2V1doSWVIcE9aSEZETVVOd1dFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "It was a fun place to spend an afternoon. There’s a nice mix of shops and places to grab a bite, and the overall vibe is relaxed and welcoming. I enjoyed walking around and checking out a few stores I hadn’t seen before. The only reason I’m giving four stars instead of five is that it felt a little crowded, and parking took longer than I expected. Other than that, it was a great experience, and I’d definitely stop by again the next time I’m in the area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It was a fun place to spend an afternoon. There’s a nice mix of shops and places to grab a bite, and the overall vibe is relaxed and welcoming. I enjoyed walking around and checking out a few stores I hadn’t seen before. The only reason I’m giving four stars instead of five is that it felt a little crowded, and parking took longer than I expected. Other than that, it was a great experience, and I’d definitely stop by again the next time I’m in the area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ryder Aldrich", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108644164096571607366/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhQ0k3B7-5v7Hkgoaq9nz9PeutNnqCgrwmlTYMUaOE3pUzLKo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-20T05:18:22.540280713Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkS2F6WmlhR1I2V1doSWVIcE9aSEZETVVOd1dFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkS2F6WmlhR1I2V1doSWVIcE9aSEZETVVOd1dFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c639ee760343:0x8defc34552d7d376"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQwN27jnGwoARdtPXUkXD740/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Sd2FrazBZV0kxYTFKVGNFWnJMV2RJWWs4dGIwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Fresh veggies, meats, and seafood along with ready-to-eat hot lunches and sushi. It's a great way to hit different stops while grocery shopping all at once. Parking is easy and free with validation. The atmosphere is chill and the staff is friendly.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Fresh veggies, meats, and seafood along with ready-to-eat hot lunches and sushi. It's a great way to hit different stops while grocery shopping all at once. Parking is easy and free with validation. The atmosphere is chill and the staff is friendly.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Karl A", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112018397692207604537/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKiwj0pXnj8dSMmxHq6janN02EL-hybwc5GAfsLx3Y-UKAyBA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-16T17:08:34.974856223Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Sd2FrazBZV0kxYTFKVGNFWnJMV2RJWWs4dGIwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Sd2FrazBZV0kxYTFKVGNFWnJMV2RJWWs4dGIwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c639ee760343:0x8defc34552d7d376"}, {"name": "places/ChIJQwN27jnGwoARdtPXUkXD740/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNQNDdEMDJnRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Went to a Culinary experience and Red Carpet event at the Noypitz restaurant inside this Plaza. Plenty of Free Parking in the plaza.Plaza.\n\nHad the opportunity to meet Raven, the singer for the Redbone Band.\n\nGreat Food, fun and amazing experience.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Went to a Culinary experience and Red Carpet event at the Noypitz restaurant inside this Plaza. Plenty of Free Parking in the plaza.Plaza.\n\nHad the opportunity to meet Raven, the singer for the Redbone Band.\n\nGreat Food, fun and amazing experience.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jose Beltran", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108281745825372155015/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdL_rANJRiNADD_9X3VVZ0Vj9j0M9KEKKhWXLr8QXuZxOpjiDr=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2024-11-27T15:01:52.887946Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNQNDdEMDJnRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "goo